item_name: Cuisinart Mini Prep Plus Food Processor Chopper Grinder DLC-2ABCHK
item_desc:
Once you try it, you’ll never want to cook again without the handy Cuisinart® Mini-Prep® Plus Processor by your side. Designed for daily kitchen duty, this processor is small in size but mighty in performance! The all-in-one SmartPower™ blade spins in one direction to chop ingredients; tap the touchpad control and it automatically reverses to grind nuts and spices. This same blade can also puree soups, and it emulsifies to make salad dressing, mayonnaise, and a countless array of other sauces. 

The work bowl holds up to 3 cups and features a built-in handle; a custom spatula is included to clear the work bowl in one clean sweep so you don't lose a single morsel. Best of all, the work bowl, blade, and spatula are all dishwasher safe, making the Cuisinart® Mini-Prep® Plus Processor an even more convenient addition to your kitchen.

Wattage Output: 300.0 watts

Appliance Capabilities: Chops, Blends, Grinds

Bowl Capacity: 3 cups

Ukuran: 23.5cm (Height) x 18cm (Width) x 13cm (Depth)
